com.neosensory.tlepredictionengine

Class TemeGeodeticConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neosensory.tlepredictionengine.TemeGeodeticConverter

  • public class TemeGeodeticConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides methods useful in converting from a true equator mean equinox (TEME) coordinate system to a geodetic (i.e. latitude/longitude/altitude) coordinate system. Algorithm credits: http://www.stltracker.com/resources/equations and https://quasar.as.utexas.edu/BillInfo/JulianDatesG.html
